I"÷<p><a class="internal-link" href="/secondbrain/neural-networks-merge-memory-and-computation">Neural networks</a> are massive <a class="internal-link" href="/secondbrain/engineering-conceptual-gateways-catalyzes-breakthroughs">conceptual gateways</a>. In <a class="internal-link" href="/secondbrain/machine-learning-often-finds-surprising-solutions">machine learning</a>, neural networks are a popular model architecture. In <a class="internal-link" href="/secondbrain/grandmother-cell-hypothesis-is-peak-sparsity">theoretical neuroscience</a>, they are a formalism for brains. In <a class="internal-link" href="/secondbrain/post-digital-computing-promises-superb-energy-efficiency">theoretical physics</a>, they are the basis of unconventional computing.</p>
